00:10:38,199 --> 00:10:39,918
Hello, Boss.

107
00:10:42,598 --> 00:10:43,638
Hi, Boss.

108
00:10:47,038 --> 00:10:47,997
Hi, Jod.

109
00:10:49,518 --> 00:10:51,758
Let's watch a movie.
