128
00:12:15,038 --> 00:12:19,798
Lilly, take care of yourself.
I'll hurry back to you.

129
00:12:19,959 --> 00:12:23,317
Leslie, don't worry about me.

130
00:12:23,478 --> 00:12:26,957
Take care, love.
I will be waiting for you!

131
00:12:27,118 --> 00:12:29,118
Good luck, baby!

132
00:12:59,358 --> 00:13:02,557
I'm Piak, and this is Thong.

133
00:13:02,719 --> 00:13:06,838
We're blood brothers,
and this is our empire.

134
00:13:08,079 --> 00:13:11,677
The owner of the cinema
owes my mother a favor,

135
00:13:11,838 --> 00:13:13,597
so he lets us stay here.

136
00:13:27,159 --> 00:13:28,118
Piak...

137
00:13:29,319 --> 00:13:33,757
are you sure I can move in here?

138
