Piak!

161
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:01,437
Look! Jod and Daeng!
The whole gang's here!

162
00:15:01,598 --> 00:15:03,757
Let's get them some iced coffee.

163
00:15:06,798 --> 00:15:09,878
- Jod and Daeng.
- Among the dangerous young men,

164
00:15:10,038 --> 00:15:13,397
the hottest gang in town
is Daeng Bireley's.

165
00:15:14,718 --> 00:15:19,157
Jod has a heart of steel,

166
00:15:19,318 --> 00:15:22,317
but if you're talking
about recklessness, it's Pu.

167
00:15:22,479 --> 00:15:27,797
The gang worked for the Chinese mafia...
Big Boss Macicau.

168
00:15:29,518 --> 00:15:31,197
Come on, this is too much!

169
00:15:31,358 --> 00:15:34,237
I've been waiting to see him
for two days and not a word!

170
00:15:35,278 --> 00:15:37,077
Calm down, chief.

171
00:15:38,038 --> 00:15:42,477
You know that lately
Boss hardly has time for us.

172
00:15:43,438 --> 00:15:44,637
He only talks to Lor now.

173
00:15:44,798 --> 00:15:46,557
- That prick Lor?
- Yes.

174
00:15:46,718 --> 00:15:49,997
