00:16:21,918 --> 00:16:23,238
That's another story.

190
00:16:26,438 --> 00:16:27,477
Now do we have a deal?

191
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:29,077
So, headmaster?

192
00:16:29,238 --> 00:16:30,477
Yes, no problem at all.

193
00:16:30,638 --> 00:16:34,397
He's such a lovely
and intelligent boy.

194
00:16:34,558 --> 00:16:38,077
Our school is honored
to have him as our new student.

195
00:16:40,158 --> 00:16:42,077
Okay, ma'am, it's done.

196
00:16:42,238 --> 00:16:45,757
Please thank your boss for me.

197
00:16:45,918 --> 00:16:46,877
Yes ma'am.

198
00:16:48,158 --> 00:16:49,837
If you need anything else,
just let me know.

199
00:16:51,318 --> 00:16:52,998
Boy, say hi to your teacher.

200
00:16:53,158 --> 00:16:54,397
Hi, teacher.

201
00:16:54,558 --> 00:16:57,277
If that is all, I'll go now.

202
00:16:57,438 --> 00:16:59,397
- Sure, headmaster.
- Goodbye.

203
00:17:13,878 --> 00:17:16,197
Hey, rookie! Come here.

204
00:17:18,519 --> 00:17:21,237
- What's your name? Where are you from?
- I'm Tui, sir.

205
00:17:21,399 --> 00:17:25,037
If you want to be in this business,
you must have a lion's heart...

206
00:17:26,158 --> 00:17:28,157
and you have to respect seniority.

207
00:17:28,318 --> 00:17:30,357
That man, he's Chief Tong.

208
00:17:31,318 --> 00:17:32,717
That one is Aad Fapah.

209
00:17:33,879 --> 00:17:35,518
That one is Sergeant Dej.

210
00:17:35,678 --> 00:17:37,597
And Madame Kimju.

211
00:17:38,718 --> 00:17:40,437
They're the Big Four.

212
00:17:40,598 --> 00:17:42,197
And that one...

213
00:17:42,358 --> 00:17:45,277
