who wants to cast Ploy.

218
00:18:01,198 --> 00:18:02,917
Hello.

219
00:18:03,078 --> 00:18:05,437
This is my nephew Tui.
He's just started working for us.

220
00:18:05,598 --> 00:18:07,717
