Why don't you pricks get him one?

228
00:18:28,598 --> 00:18:30,557
How did you train your men, huh?

229
00:18:37,278 --> 00:18:39,757
Excuse me,
Big Boss is expecting me.

230
00:18:59,518 --> 00:19:02,317
Big Boss,
this is Daeng and his friends.

231
00:19:03,478 --> 00:19:05,477
For men like us,

232
00:19:05,638 --> 00:19:08,917
the word "gangsters"
is more meaningful than people think.

233
00:19:09,078 --> 00:19:11,637
It doesn't matter how many
people we manage to beat up,

234
00:19:11,798 --> 00:19:14,597
people still call us
"hooligans" or "thugs."

235
00:19:14,758 --> 00:19:19,557
But to me, gangsters and thugs
are two different species.

236
00:19:20,518 --> 00:19:25,117
For us, to be a gangster
means you're a part of...

237
00:19:25,278 --> 00:19:26,717
a family.

238
00:19:43,638 --> 00:19:44,865
Right, I'll draw the number now.

239
00:19:51,318 --> 00:19:52,277
Number 10!

240
00:19:54,038 --> 00:19:56,917
Shit, the house always wins!

241
00:19:57,078 --> 00:19:59,157
Are you screwing me?
I'm not paying!

242
00:20:04,998 --> 00:20:05,957
Hey!

243
00:20:07,518 --> 00:20:09,397
You lose, you pay up.

244
00:20:12,398 --> 00:20:15,197
Daeng, you think you can
boss me around?

245
00:20:19,557 --> 00:20:20,877
Let's go!

246
00:20:22,678 --> 00:20:25,877
- Forget it.
- Cheaters!

247
00:20:26,038 --> 00:20:28,317
The brothers always told me

248
00:20:28,477 --> 00:20:32,117
that a gangster's worth is his courage.

249
00:20:32,278 --> 00:20:35,797
That's why Jod has pledged
his life on Daeng Bireley,

250
00:20:35,958 --> 00:20:38,837
even though Jod was
more senior in years and experience.

251
00:20:50,878 --> 00:20:53,797
Hey, that looks kinda fun.

252
00:20:55,998 --> 00:20:57,477
Dam, look there.

253
00:21:36,357 --> 00:21:37,877
Running away, Jod?

254
00:22:01,798 --> 00:22:02,797
Stop!

255
00:22:38,558 --> 00:22:41,197
I don't know
why you guys helped me.

256
00:22:42,358 --> 00:22:43,556
Thank you anyway.

257
00:22:48,917 --> 00:22:49,876
I'm Jod.

258
00:22:54,718 --> 00:22:55,677
What the?

